      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Every mechanical component performs with the precision of a new machine. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than the finest, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
