    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a car that doesn't just transport you, but transforms the very air around you. This masterpiece of engineering is a love letter to the open road, draped in a silhouette that captures the golden hour even at midnight. Inside, the scent of hand-stitched leather and polished wood whispers stories of coastal drives and moonlit getaways. It doesn't just run; it breathes with a rhythmic precision that makes every gear shift feel like a heartbeat. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a preserved moment in time, a pristine soul waiting for its next curator to write the next chapter of its legendary journey.",
      "price": 48900.0,
